sequenceDiagram
    participant User as You (Voice)
    participant FX as JavaFX Client<br/>(Java 21)
    participant Whisper as Whisper AI
    participant LLM as GPT-5 Nano
    participant MCP as MCP Server<br/>(Java 25 + Spring AI)
    participant OQ as osqueryi

    User->>FX: "Computer, run a level 1 diagnostic"
    FX->>Whisper: Audio bytes
    Whisper-->>FX: "run a level 1 diagnostic"

    FX->>LLM: User prompt + tool definitions
    Note over LLM: Matches prompt to<br/>getSystemHealthSummary()

    LLM->>MCP: Tool call: getSystemHealthSummary
    Note over MCP: Virtual threads spawn<br/>5 parallel queries

    par CPU query
        MCP->>OQ: osqueryi --json "SELECT ... processes"
        OQ-->>MCP: JSON result
    and Memory query
        MCP->>OQ: osqueryi --json "SELECT ... resident_size"
        OQ-->>MCP: JSON result
    and Disk query
        MCP->>OQ: osqueryi --json "SELECT ... mounts"
        OQ-->>MCP: JSON result
    and Network query
        MCP->>OQ: osqueryi --json "SELECT ... sockets"
        OQ-->>MCP: JSON result
    and Temperature query
        MCP->>OQ: osqueryi --json "SELECT ... sensors"
        OQ-->>MCP: JSON result
    end

    MCP-->>LLM: Combined system health JSON
    Note over LLM: Synthesizes natural<br/>language summary

    LLM-->>FX: Streamed response (Flux)
    Note over FX: Text appears line<br/>by line in UI
    FX-->>User: "Level 1 diagnostic complete..."
